Awesome choice! A simple 2D racing game in Java is a fun way to learn about:
Graphics and animation (javax.swing, java.awt)
Game loop mechanics
Collision detection
Keyboard controls


🏁 Project Plan: Simple Racing Game in Java
🔧 Tech Stack
Java (core)
Swing for GUI
AWT for 2D graphics


🎮 Features
Top-down or side-scrolling race view
Car controlled by keyboard arrows
Obstacle avoidance (e.g., traffic cones or other cars)
Score/Distance counter
Basic Game Over screen